---
title: Braised Chicken Breast and Mushrooms with Buttery Smashed Potatoes
description: Here comes the flavour of a slow-cooked homemade supper, in a fraction of the time! Savoury mushrooms make this tender chicken dish taste like it's been bubbling away on the stove all day.
